Interface OMMToCEntry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    OMMAttributeListBlock, OMMBlock, OMMIdentifierBlock, OMMSemanticsBlock, OMMStructureBlock
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OMMAttributeListBlockImpl, OMMBlockImpl, OMMBlockRestImpl, OMMIdentifierBlockImpl, OMMSemanticsBlockImpl, OMMStructureBlockImpl

    public interface OMMToCEntry
    Contains all meta data information of a OMM table of contents entry.
